{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><h2 id=\"mFiX1\"><span class=\"ne-text\">快速插入图片</span></h2><p id=\"ua9dbc221\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ua39e59b7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如要你要在文档插入图片，可以选择在卡片插入中选择“图片”，还支持直接将图片拖入到编辑器，或将图片直接复制到编辑器中，这样也可以直接上传图片。</span></p><p id=\"uadba24c2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u07a0c993\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u2fd86025\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634096371555-05aa8a55-d5e2-4e3a-a2a7-91a839bf1d2b.png\" width=\"320\" id=\"AcrCE\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u87907ad4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u5ed35844\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">同时支持以下快捷键（支持中文，拼音和英文）</span></p><p id=\"uf2c57391\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ua900b471\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/图片</span></code></p><p id=\"u3df44c5c\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/tupian</span></code></p><p id=\"ueb916b8b\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/tp</span></code></p><p id=\"u4af5e685\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/image</span></code></p><h2 id=\"hm4P8\"></h2><h2 id=\"nAps9\"><span class=\"ne-text\">功能简介</span></h2><p id=\"u4436acc8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u405ea238\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过图片工具栏和图片右侧设置面板，可以修改图片大小、样式，可以对图片进行裁剪、旋转，还可以添加图片描述、链接。</span></p><p id=\"u428e4376\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"uce1bf0a4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">将鼠标悬浮到图片上，可唤醒图片工具栏；点击图片工具栏上“...”，可打开图片右侧设置面板进行更多操作。</span></p><p id=\"u2a304245\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21758220/1637302044584-b3ce0612-c555-43f8-879d-9c43b2f84587.png\" width=\"1303\" id=\"u6f0f0791\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u006ef4e5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u82d6bcf0\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"kGPdP\"><span class=\"ne-text\">修改图片尺寸</span></h4><p id=\"ub7e9f7b4\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u4b460489\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">有 3 种不同的方式修改图片尺寸：</span></p><p id=\"ue6e310b0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u66634719\"><span class=\"ne-text\">选中图片，拖动图片 4 个角可修改图片大小</span></li></ol><p id=\"u93257a93\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"uaacdbb26\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/gif/21758220/1637302674509-6bc9a095-c899-4107-9e97-d9b229a35eec.gif\" width=\"648\" id=\"ud1a19b5b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u6da6f851\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"2\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u87a3b5c9\"><span class=\"ne-text\">图片工具栏或右侧面板设置图片宽和高</span></li></ol><p id=\"u5d47d111\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"3\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u84c571c6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在图片右侧面板上设置图片百分比</span></li></ol><p id=\"u4a9e75a9\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"woW3A\"></h4><h4 id=\"vjTc0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">调整图片样式</span></h4><p id=\"u903581d5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u9d5f9b0b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">鼠标悬浮在图片上，点击图片工具栏上「图片样式」按钮，在下拉菜单中选中一个样式即可。</span></p><p id=\"ua94f8ee7\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21758220/1637302043902-39d8e707-4173-4610-aef7-d5d502df1686.png\" width=\"648\" id=\"u3ef38802\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u6c44ea4d\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"ZRWvJ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">裁剪</span></h4><p id=\"u67678c8c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ufb6dbe95\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">鼠标悬浮在图片上，在图片工具栏上点击「图片裁剪」按钮，进入裁剪模式，裁剪图片后，点击非图片区域即可完成裁剪。</span></p><p id=\"ue3471c2c\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/gif/21758220/1637302042942-8dd242e6-7b5e-46db-b31f-3c0a034904da.gif\" width=\"648\" id=\"ue25ff61b\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u753967b3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"HtTcz\"><span class=\"ne-text\">旋转</span></h4><p id=\"u4b880ecd\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u2c85e8eb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">鼠标悬浮在图片上，在图片工具栏上点击「逆时针旋转 90 度」按钮即可。</span></p><p id=\"u659d500f\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21758220/1637302043961-ac76da3f-56eb-4a14-9ceb-72983cd6476e.png\" width=\"648\" id=\"ub4889aa2\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"p6bCV\"></h4><h4 id=\"F3FRw\"><span class=\"ne-text\">其他功能</span></h4><p id=\"u0769d7c0\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ucb2393de\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">图片还支持如下功能：</span></p><p id=\"u13c9a206\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u1e5a2441\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">添加图片描述</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：鼠标悬浮在图片上，在图片工具栏上点击「图片描述」，在图片底部编辑图片描述即可。</span></li></ol><p id=\"u4bf8f705\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21758220/1637302046255-37393574-a426-4d84-aa1e-3b8c203d01d9.png\" width=\"648\" id=\"ube4fdcb8\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><ol start=\"2\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u670e2cc9\"><span class=\"ne-text\">添加图片链接：鼠标悬浮在图片上，在图片工具栏上点击「...」，在图片右侧面板上添加图片链接地址即可。</span></li></ol><p id=\"ud41a4ba8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"3\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u292b0c3d\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置图片与上下内容的间距：鼠标悬浮在图片上，在图片工具栏上点击「...」，在图片右侧面板上修改图片与上下内容间距即可。</span></li></ol><h2 id=\"kELeY\"></h2><h2 id=\"oYvyG\"><span class=\"ne-text\">常见问题</span></h2><h4 id=\"mGfpO\"></h4><h4 id=\"aI1Kb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入图片有大小和格式限制吗？</span></h4><div id=\"GpZAx\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/rms0so\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/rms0so</a></div><p id=\"u36211cf3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900810,
  "title": "如何插入图片"
}